1. install and configure puppetmaster
2. install and configure puppet client
3. install puppet modules: github (vcsrepo) and mysql (mysql) ---> install in server and client
4. Requirements/nodes.pp (/etc/puppet/manifests/)
5. Requirements/site.pp (/etc/puppet/manifests/)
6. Requirements/cvsanaly.pp (/etc/puppet/modules/cvsanaly/cvsanaly.pp)


- Requirements are in REQUIREMENTS file into Requirements directory

- Command to check new configurations (change it test1.domain.test1 for your puppetmaster's name)
puppetd --server test1.domain.test1 --test
